name: Capybara unboxer
description:
The one, The only: capybara unboxer!

Unbox over 40 different types of capybaras ranging from common to legendary!

Note: I made this project to learn unity, it's likely more buggy and more unoptimized then cyberpunk 2077 on release. If you let me know what the bugs are I'll try my best to fix them, in the mean time enjoy unbox your capy's!
